definitions.definition: Belonging or relating to the branch of Islam based on the Qur'an , the Kutub al-Sittah (the hadiths which record the Sunnah ) and that places emphasis on the Sahabah .

main_definition: Belonging or relating to the branch of Islam based on the Qur'an , the Kutub al-Sittah (the hadiths which record the Sunnah ) and that places emphasis on the Sahabah .
